# Group Patient Prescription
## List Prescriptions [/api/v1/prescriptions{?per_page}]
### List Prescriptions [GET]

Gets all the Prescriptions for the current logged in user.
Admin, Practitioner role: Gets all the prescriptions.
Patient role: Gets prescriptions assigned or created by current Patient.

+ Parameters
    + per_page: `3` (number, optional) - Enables pagination and set items per page.

+ Request Example

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer {{ ACCESS_TOKEN }}
            X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
            Content-Type: application/json

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

    + Body

