## Get Prescription [/api/v1/prescriptions/{prescription_id}]
### Get Prescription [GET]

Gets a Prescription associated to a Patient.

+ Require Admin, Practitioner or logged in Patient matching requested patient_id. Prescription must belong to Patient.

+ Parameters
    + patient_id: `1` (number, required) - Must be a valid ID.
    + prescription_id: `2` (number, required) - Must be a valid ID.

+ Request Example

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer {{ ACCESS_TOKEN }}
            X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
            Content-Type: application/json

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

